room_title: Escape room "Treasury Take Down" by Coral Springs Escape Rooms in Miami
room_description:
Your team and you have managed to break into The Vault. The guards will be gone for one hour before they are back for their next round along The Vault. This means you have one hour to crack the safes and be gone with all the wealth you’ll ever need.
Does your team have the skills to crack the safe and be rich beyond your wildest dreams? Team Building is the “keyword”. There is now only one concern, to open the safe door and be sure that you are gone before the guards are back.
